  "text": "A supervised analysis was also performed to determine genes that were significantly differentially expressed between pre-and post-epigenetic treatment in clinical samples using significance analysis ofg microarrays. This method involves testing each gene one at a time and then performing 100 permutation tests to estimate the false-discovery rate that arises from input genes [CITATION_1] . We selected the number of significant genes corresponding to a target false-discovery rate of 0.16.",
